      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution spot-check against PIV measurements",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry data from the literature (Hariharan et al. 2011) was used to spot-check near-wall velocity gradients in the volute region. The CFD model reproduced peak wall shear stress within 12% of measured values, satisfying the MRL 2 threshold.",
      "comparedAgainst": "https://uofa.net/morrison/data/fda-generic-pump-experimental-hemolysis",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/morrison/activity/piv-comparison-run-2024-11"
