      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V and FDA-recognized quality management system; version-controlled simulation scripts.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 was used under an ISO 13485-compliant QMS. Solver release notes and regression test reports were reviewed. Simulation scripts were version-controlled in Git with tagged release corresponding to this study."
