      "rationale": "Three meshes (1.8 M, 4.2 M, 9.7 M cells) were generated with uniform refinement ratio r=1.5. Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI of 3.8% on NIH at the nominal operating point (3.5 L/min, 3000 RPM), satisfying the 5% criterion. The 4.2 M mesh was selected for production runs."
    },
