      "rationale": "The primary QoI is the normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) and derived relative hemolysis index (RH). These quantities are the direct regulatory acceptance metrics specified in FDA guidance for CPB devices. No intermediate transformations are required; the model output is compared directly against the acceptance criterion RH < 1."
