    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. The primary validation result demonstrated MAPE of 9.3% on NIH across five operating points, satisfying the 15% threshold. All RH values were below 1.0. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
